'''Tony Bennett''' (born '''Anthony Dominick Benedetto'''; August 3, 1926) is an [[United States|American]] [[singer]] of [[traditional pop music|popular music]], [[pop standards|standards]] and [[jazz]]. 
I '''Tony Bennett''' (born '''Anthony Dominick Benedetto'''; August 3, 1926) metung yang [[talakanta]ng [[:en:United States|Americanu]] ning [[:en:traditional pop music|musicang pop]],  [[:en:pop standards|standards]] ampong [[jazz]].   

Raised in [[New York City]], Bennett began singing at an early age. He fought in the final stages of World War II as an [[infantry rifleman|infantryman]] with the [[U.S. Army]] in the  [[European Theatre]]. Afterwards, he developed his singing technique, signed with [[Columbia Records]], and had his first number one popular song with "[[Because of You (1940 song)|Because of You]]" in 1951. Several top hits such as "[[Rags to Riches (song)|Rags to Riches]]" followed in the early 1950s.  Bennett then further refined his approach to encompass [[jazz singing]]. He reached an artistic peak in the late 1950s with albums such as ''[[The Beat of My Heart]]'' and ''[[Basie Swings, Bennett Sings]].'' In 1962, Bennett recorded his [[signature song]], "[[I Left My Heart in San Francisco]]". His career and his personal life then suffered an extended downturn during the height of the [[rock music]] era.
Meragul ya king [[New York Lakanbalen]] i Bennett, at malati ya pamu, magkanta ne. Linaban ya aniang mayayari ne ing Kaduang Gerang Meto Yatu antimong [[:en:infantry rifleman|infantryman]] king [[U.S. Army]] keng [[:en:European Theatre|Gera king Europa]]. Kaibat, meyalkus (''developed'') ya ing istilu na king pamagkanta, pinirma yang contrata king [[Columbia Records]], at linual ya ing minuna nang kantang mig-''number one'' aniang 1951, ing "[[:en:Because of You (1940 song)|Because of You]]". Mitukian ya pa iti kareng aliwang sinikat a ''hit'' aniang decadang 1950, antimo ing "[[:en:Rags to Riches (song)|Rags to Riches]]". Lalu yang meging maleparan ing saklo ning kayang pamagkanta, at liban ne murin ing [[:en:jazz singing|pamagkantang jazz]]. Miras ya king metung a taluktuk ning kayang carera aniang tauli nang dake ning decadang 1950 kapamilatan da reng album antimo ing ''[[:en:The Beat of My Heart|The Beat of My Heart]]'' and ''[[:en:Basie Swings, Bennett Sings|Basie Swings, Bennett Sings]].'' Kanitang 1962, mibulalag ya ing kayang "[[:en:signature song|signature song]]", ing "[[:en:I Left My Heart in San Francisco|I Left My Heart in San Francisco]]". Kaibat na niti, limbug yang maluat ing kayang carera ampong bieng personal aniang kasikatan ning panaun ning [[:en:rock music|musicang rock]]          

Bennett staged a remarkable comeback in the late 1980s and 1990s, putting out [[gold record]] albums again and expanding his audience to the [[MTV Generation]] while keeping his musical style intact. He remains a popular and critically praised recording artist and concert performer in the 2000s. Bennett has won fifteen [[Grammy Award]]s, two [[Emmy Award]]s, been named an [[NEA Jazz Masters|NEA Jazz Master]] and a [[Kennedy Center Honors|Kennedy Center Honoree]]. He has sold over 50 million records worldwide. Bennett is also a serious and accomplished [[painting|painter]], creating works under the name '''Benedetto''' that are on permanent public display in several institutions.
Mika makapagmulala yang pamagbalik ing carera nang Bennett aniang tauli nang dake ning decadang 1980 ampong decadang 1990, at migpalual yang pasibayung album a ''[[:en:gold record|gold record]]'' at melapad la reng kayang makiramdam kareng ibat king [[:en:MTV Generation|MTV Generation]], kabang menatili ya ing kayang istilo king musica. Angga ngening kapanauanan a 2000, sikat ya pa murin at pupurian da reng criticu antimong metung a talakantang mag-''record'' ampong lalage kareng conciertu. Sinambut neng labing limang [[Grammy Award]] ampong aduang [[Emmy Award]] i Benett, at mirinan yang galal antimong [[:en:NEA Jazz Masters|NEA Jazz Master]] ampong [[:en:Kennedy Center Honors|Kennedy Center Honoree]]. MIras nong 50 miliun deng apisali nang plaka king mabilug a yatu. Metung ya muring seriosu ampong biasang pintor, at maglalang yang obra lalam ning lagiung '''Benedetto''', a makapakit kareng miayaliwang institucion. 

